attributionInfo.brokerName: Century 21 Hometown Realty, Arroyo Grande Office

data.description: Don't worry about paying for electricity. Homeowner OWNED SOLAR worth over 30k included in sale. In the heart of the Arroyo Grande, 341 Alder Street offers a rare opportunity to own a piece of California's coastal paradise. This charming home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1,522 +-/ square feet of living space. Presenting granite countertops, and travertine tile in the kitchen, bathrooms, and fireplace, you will also enjoy beautiful bamboo flooring throughout. A private and spacious backyard offers fruit and avocado trees and is the perfect place for entertaining and relaxing. The Flag lot driveway is long enough to park all your toys and safe for kids to play off the street. It also has energy-efficient windows, and a new water heater, other upgrades include a new polyurethane finish in the garage, new carpet in 2 of the bedrooms, a new fence, dual shower heads in the master bathroom and the backyard is jacuzzi ready with electricity set up. Situated in a desirable neighborhood close to schools, shopping, dining, and the beach. This is one opportunity you do not want to miss!
